lead_paragraph: A flop shot that required feel. A wedge to a back pin that he had to trust. Tiger Woods followed those two birdies with a perfect 6-iron that he wanted to be even better, urging it to move "one yard ... one yard!"

headline.print_headline: More Time Needed Before Tiger Woods Is Judged by His Scores
